NAME
    Serializer - lightweight perl serializer

SYNOPSIS
        use Serializer qw(thaw freeze);
    
        my $frozen = freeze ([1, 2, 3]);
        my $unfrozen = thaw ($frozen);

DESCRIPTION
    Simple lightweight recursive pure-perl data serializer. Takes into
    account UTF-8 scalars. Works just like thaw() and freeze() in Storable.

EXPORT
    Doesn't export anything by default.

SEE ALSO
    Storable, JSON::XS, Data::MessagePack

